Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.96,0:23:12.49,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&HCB3B17&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur7.5\fad(150,150)}When I cried and had no place to go?\N門另一邊聽到的是你嗎
